      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">237.7003</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a)  Use the following clauses in all mortuary service solicitations and contracts, except do not use the clauses at 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383573"
                  href="252.237-7004.dita#DFARS_252.237-7004">252.237-7004</xref>
            , Area of Performance, in solicitations or contracts that include port of entry requirements:</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(1)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383568"
                  href="252.237-7003.dita#DFARS_252.237-7003">252.237-7003</xref>
            , Requirements, (insert activities authorized to place orders in paragraph (e) of the clause).</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(2)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383573"
                  href="252.237-7004.dita#DFARS_252.237-7004">252.237-7004</xref>
            , Area of Performance.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(3)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383578"
                  href="252.237-7005.dita#DFARS_252.237-7005">252.237-7005</xref>
            , Performance and Delivery.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(4)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383583"
                  href="252.237-7006.dita#DFARS_252.237-7006">252.237-7006</xref>
            , Subcontracting.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(5)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383588"
                  href="252.237-7007.dita#DFARS_252.237-7007">252.237-7007</xref>
            , Termination for Default.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(6)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383593"
                  href="252.237-7008.dita#DFARS_252.237-7008">252.237-7008</xref>
            , Group Interment.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(7)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383598"
                  href="252.237-7009.dita#DFARS_252.237-7009">252.237-7009</xref>
            , Permits.</p>
         <p outputclass="List2" class="- topic/p ">(8)  
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="i1383612"
                  href="252.237-7011.dita#DFARS_252.237-7011">252.237-7011</xref>
            , Preparation History.</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b)  Use the clause at FAR 52.245-1, Government Property, with its Alternate I, in solicitations and contracts that include port of entry requirements.</p>
